{"tid":2439502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德國學者指控新彊「強迫勞動」 被當地企業控告造謠 內地律師警告：罪成或再不能在中國坐高鐵","createTime":"2021-03-09T09:49:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T12:42:02.000Z","uid":321059,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3b82f79206b10f2b0021a5667ec1139e8b9de81c","tid":2439502,"uid":321059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T09:49:57.000Z","msg":"內地官媒報導，新疆部分企業和民眾將向當地法院起訴德國學者鄭國恩。理由是他在網上散佈謠言，指新疆對少數民族實行強迫勞動等，令民眾聲譽受損，連帶打擊當地棉花及棉花製品出口。<br />\n<br />\n有內地律師指就算鄭國恩被定罪，要跨國執行裁決亦有難度，<span class=\"red\">後果可能是他朝入境中國時不能坐高鐵。</span><br />\n<br />\nSource: 眾新聞中國組<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RPThyYG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRPThyYG.jpg&h=b8ce081c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n學者：我真係好撚驚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2373761c1dbdf6786a9b3216b07e81d5c5508308","tid":2439502,"uid":321059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T09:51:40.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"orange\">請支持眾新聞中國組</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkcnews/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkcnews%2F&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy4429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=945bdab3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkcnews/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"666418d574d5750e691e771e3bccd70b5f76f69b","tid":2439502,"uid":44646,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T09:53:01.000Z","msg":"點解唔去德國告？"},{"pid":"0ec7a6f4f86bdf20d915f0344997c0008067003f","tid":2439502,"uid":3553,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":